Title: Glimpses of Bengal Selected from the Letters of Sir Rabindranath Tagore  
Author: Rabindranath Tagore
Hardcover: 168 pages
Publisher: TREDITION CLASSICS (December 12, 2012)
Language: English
ISBN-10: 3849160386
ISBN-13: 978-3849160388

Description:
This book is part of the TREDITION CLASSICS. It contains classical literature works from over two thousand years. Most of these titles have been out of print and off the bookstore shelves for decades. The book series is intended to preserve the cultural legacy and to promote the timeless works of classical literature. Readers of a TREDITION CLASSICS book support the mission to save many of the amazing works of world literature from oblivion. With this series, tradition intends to make thousands of international literature classics available in printed format again - worldwide
